com.mindfusion.scheduling

Enum PreviewTextKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<PreviewTextKey>
      • com.mindfusion.scheduling.PreviewTextKey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<PreviewTextKey>

    public enum PreviewTextKey
extends java.lang.Enum<PreviewTextKey>
    Contains the key for various texts in the built-in Print Preview form.

    Members of this enumeration can be used as keys in the getCustomPreviewTexts dictionary of the PrintOptions class.
